org.eclipse.modisco.jee.webapp.webapp23
Interface WebAppType

public interface WebAppType

A representation of the model object 'Web App Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Icon
  • Display Name
  • Description
  • Distributable
  • Context Param
  • Filter
  • Filter Mapping
  • Listener
  • Servlet
  • Servlet Mapping
  • Session Config
  • Mime Mapping
  • Welcome File List
  • Error Page
  • Taglib
  • Resource Env Ref
  • Resource Ref
  • Security Constraint
  • Login Config
  • Security Role
  • Env Entry
  • Ejb Ref
  • Ejb Local Ref
  • Id
